org.eclipse.scada.configuration.world.deployment

Interface ChangeEntry

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ChangeEntryImpl

    public interface ChangeEntry
    A representation of the model object 'Change Entry'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Author
    • Date
    • Description
    • Version

    See Also:
    DeploymentPackage.getChangeEntry()
